OL,3,C'I might be late home' - stadium fire
OL,4,Cvictim's final words to family
OL,6,FThe family of one of the victims of
OL,7,Fthe Bradford City stadium fire have
OL,8,Frecalled how he told them "I might be
OL,9,Flate" before he left home for the last
OL,10,Ftime.
OL,12,FDerek Dempsey, 46, was among 56 people
OL,13,Fwho lost their lives when the club's
OL,14,FValley Parade ground was destroyed by
OL,15,Fa huge blaze on 11 May 1985.
OL,17,FCommemorations to mark the 40th
OL,18,Fanniversary of the disaster will take
OL,19,Fplace in the city this weekend.
