OL,3,C'I might be late home' - stadium fire
OL,4,Cvictim's final words to family
OL,6,FMr Dempsey, a long-time Bradford fan,
OL,7,Fhad gone to watch the Bantams play
OL,8,FLincoln City after his side had
OL,9,Fclinched the Division Two title.
OL,11,FHis daughter, Georgie, said: "He was
OL,12,Freally excited, he was giddy. He was
OL,13,Flike a kid. And then, when it was time
OL,14,Ffor him to go, he came and gave my mum
OL,15,Fa proper kiss and he picked her up and
OL,16,Fspun her round."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/7
