OL,3,C'I might be late home' - stadium fire
OL,4,Cvictim's final words to family
OL,6,FMr Dempsey's widow Glenys added: "He
OL,7,Fgot to the back door and he turned
OL,8,Fround and he said to me, 'don't start
OL,9,Fcooking at the normal time because I
OL,10,Fmight be late home, because there will
OL,11,Fbe a lot of people'.
OL,13,F"And he never came home at all."
OL,15,FNormally taking his place in the kop
OL,16,Fat Valley Parade, Mr Dempsey's family
OL,17,Fsay he had "treated himself" to a
OL,18,Fticket in the main stand for what
OL,19,Fshould have been a day of celebrations.
