OL,3,C'I might be late home' - stadium fire
OL,4,Cvictim's final words to family
OL,6,FAt 3.44pm that day, as a dull game
OL,7,Fapproached half-time, a discarded
OL,8,Fcigarette started a blaze which,
OL,9,Fwithin less than five minutes, had
OL,10,Fengulfed the entire stand.
OL,12,FMr Demspey's body was later found
OL,13,Ftrapped at a turnstile, along with
OL,14,Fthat of one of his friends.
OL,16,FGlenys and Georgie Dempsey were at
OL,17,Fhome following the game on the radio
OL,18,Fwhen the fire took hold.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/7
