OL,3,C'I might be late home' - stadium fire
OL,4,Cvictim's final words to family
OL,6,F"I was upstairs doing homework and I
OL,7,Fwas listening to the match on the
OL,8,Fradio," Georgie said.
OL,10,F"Mum said she knew (her husband had
OL,11,Fdied) straight away."
OL,13,FGlenys said: "It was like a light had
OL,14,Fbeen switched off."
OL,16,FGeorgie said as the hours passed she
OL,17,Fwent into denial.
OL,19,F"I said 'he'll be busy, he'll be
OL,20,Fhelping people'. I was just trying to
OL,21,Fpretend to myself it wasn't happening."
