OL,3,C'I might be late home' - stadium fire
OL,4,Cvictim's final words to family
OL,6,FGlenys said friends of the family went
OL,7,Fon a frantic search of several
OL,8,Fhospitals hoping to find her husband.
OL,10,FThe only possession of Mr Demspey's
OL,11,Fthat survived was a pendant of St
OL,12,FChristopher given to him by his wife,
OL,13,Fwhich she wears to this day.
OL,15,FGlenys and Georgie, who now live on
OL,16,Fthe Isle of Man, visited Valley Parade
OL,17,Fas the anniversary of the tragedy
OL,18,Fapproached.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/7
