OL,3,C'I might be late home' - stadium fire
OL,4,Cvictim's final words to family
OL,6,FSpeaking at the ground Glenys said:
OL,7,F"It's bittersweet but it's good...
OL,8,Fit's nice to come back to the ground
OL,9,Fand see it in its current glory."
OL,11,FGeorgie added: "It feels a bit like a
OL,12,Fhug.
OL,14,F"It needs remembering, it deserves to
OL,15,Fbe remembered, and being here is a bit
OL,16,Flike flying the flag for dad and I'm
OL,17,Fproud to do that."
OL,19,F"It is important that it is remembered
OL,20,Fand that people who perhaps weren't
OL,21,Fborn when it happened know about it."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/7
